A survey that removes pointless regulations
The poll on Absurdity of the Year is part of the business competition for the fourth time.
Some pointless regulations have already been abolished.
The infamous winner of the next edition of the Absurdity of the Year poll was the obligation to bring documents to the office, which are also accessible to officials online.
