At the Land Fund in Pilsen, the police made an arrest during a public tender
The anti-corruption police made arrests in the building of the Land Fund in Pilsen in recent days.
The detectives put handcuffs on a local entrepreneur in the media sphere and real estate dealer Luboš G.
He allegedly tried to manipulate the ongoing public competition to settle restitution claims so that the land offered in the competition was won by a specific interested party.
